        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHi all,\n\nI have to push this one as a new code review, as I have problem to submit another patch to the previous one(https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/83423/) after rebase, complaining about one code review is already closed. \n\nCould you please review the change? One concern i have is around the thread in PnfEventReadyDmaapClient, it causes all the following activities initialised twice in my integration test. that's why I change that logic. Please take a look and let me know whether that will work or not. Thank you!",
